PathnamesPage.description:
Kua whakamāoritia hoki ngā ingoa ara.

Mēnā kei te whakamahi koe i te reo taketake Ingarihi, ka kite koe i /en/pathnames i te pae wāhitau pūtirotiro o tēnei whārangi.

Mēnā ka huri koe i te reo ki te Tiamana, ka whakamāoritia te URL e ai ki te reo (/de/pfadnamen).
PathnamesPage.title: Ingoa Ara
